description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Cooter purrs with a rating of 79, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 79, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 3 for East, 5 for South, and Box for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90791-13542-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [79 Votes, Top 9% Rating]
